  ('legacy-sco-141', '140', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_001', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Explain why people might want to reduce the warming effect of the sun', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-142', '141', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_002', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Name one thing people can build to minimize the warming effect of the sun – could be umbrellas, canopies, and tents', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-143', '142', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_003', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Explain one thing (asking questions, making observations, and gathering information) that people might do to solve problems like the warming effect of the sun', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-144', '143', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_004', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Tell one way that the child may protect themself and their belongings from the sun, or the rain', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-145', '144', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_005', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Design a structure that will keep the rain or sun off their play things at their house (this could be making a drawing of something that would keep the rain or sun off their play things)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-146', '145', 'science', 'K', 'Weather and Climate', 'SC_GK_ST3_ELO2_K_006', '[ELO2 - Knowledge] Build a structure that will keep the rain or sun off their play things at their house (to do this, the children might use recycled objects to make a shelter for their toy car, or tricycle – whatever is relevant to their experience)', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Weather and Climate', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00', '2026-01-01T02:00:17.75147+00:00'),
