  ('legacy-sco-904', '2605', 'science', '6', 'Forces and Interactions', 'SC_G6_ST5_ELO1_S_002', '[ELO1 - Skills] Create a balloon rocket model to test Newton''s third law that for every reaction there is an equal and opposite reaction.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Forces and Interactions', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-905', '2606', 'science', '6', 'Forces and Interactions', 'SC_G6_ST5_ELO1_S_003', '[ELO1 - Skills] Design and build a unique toy car to test how we can absorb an equal and opposite force acting on colliding objects.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Forces and Interactions', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00'),
  ('legacy-sco-906', '2607', 'science', '6', 'Forces and Interactions', 'SC_G6_ST5_ELO1_S_004', '[ELO1 - Skills] Draw free-body diagrams to represent opposing forces.', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Forces and Interactions', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00', '2026-01-01T04:40:40.068592+00:00'),
